<paragraph id="8BDC369AFFABFFC5FCD7FBABFCAB2069" blockId="30.[809,1425,1052,1135]" lastBlockId="31.[163,780,197,280]" lastPageId="31" lastPageNumber="616" pageId="30" pageNumber="615">
<emphasis id="B917EA88FFABFFC4FCD7FBABFC092540" box="[809,942,1052,1073]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="615">Diagnosis:</emphasis>
Dorsal scutum beta-type, long and unarmed legs (
<figureCitation id="13582A1FFFABFFC4FC1CFB8DFBEF2521" box="[994,1096,1082,1104]" captionStart="Figure 19" captionStartId="30.[145,225,1846,1868]" captionTargetBox="[305,1265,1171,1807]" captionTargetId="figure-460@30.[305,1265,1171,1807]" captionTargetPageId="30" captionText="Figure 19. Cynorta pustulata, male holotype (SMF RII 186/5). A, dorsal view. B, postero dorsal view. C, original label. Photos courtesy Abel Pérez." pageId="30" pageNumber="615">Fig. 19A</figureCitation>
). Area I with low rounded tubercles and area 
<collectionCode id="ED72AE5FFFABFFC4FBFCFBEDFB87251E" box="[1026,1056,1114,1135]" pageId="30" pageNumber="615">III</collectionCode>
with long and acuminate spines (
<figureCitation id="13582A1FFFAAFFC5FF55FF72FEAD21AB" box="[171,266,197,219]" captionStart="Figure 19" captionStartId="30.[145,225,1846,1868]" captionTargetBox="[305,1265,1171,1807]" captionTargetId="figure-460@30.[305,1265,1171,1807]" captionTargetPageId="30" captionText="Figure 19. Cynorta pustulata, male holotype (SMF RII 186/5). A, dorsal view. B, postero dorsal view. C, original label. Photos courtesy Abel Pérez." pageId="31" pageNumber="616">Fig. 19B</figureCitation>
). Large spots scattered in all dorsal scutum, except a part of the carapace anterior to ocularium. Free tergites with equally spaced yellow dots (
<figureCitation id="13582A1FFFAAFFC5FD5FFEB5FD5A2069" box="[673,765,258,280]" captionStart="Figure 19" captionStartId="30.[145,225,1846,1868]" captionTargetBox="[305,1265,1171,1807]" captionTargetId="figure-460@30.[305,1265,1171,1807]" captionTargetPageId="30" captionText="Figure 19. Cynorta pustulata, male holotype (SMF RII 186/5). A, dorsal view. B, postero dorsal view. C, original label. Photos courtesy Abel Pérez." pageId="31" pageNumber="616">Fig. 19A</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
